sy%20victory%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20Their%20confidence%20was%20compounded%20manifold%20by%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20consecration%20as%20well%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-tejashwi-yadav-to-take-same-flight-amid-opposition-outreach-buzz-5821198%5C%22%3EBihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar's%3C%2Fa%3E%20somersault%20from%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20to%20the%20NDA.%20The%20opposition%20alliance%20had%20been%20in%20total%20disarray%20back%20then.%20But%20a%20substantial%20turnout%20drop%20in%20the%20initial%20phase%20of%20voting%20was%20perhaps%20the%20first%20indication%20that%20things%20were%20not%20moving%20in%20the%20right%20direction%20for%20the%20party.%20The%20turnout%20didn't%20improve%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20phases%20either.%20As%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-election-2024-lok-sabha-results-as-bjp-falls-short-of-majority-2-coalition-era-veterans-emerge-kingmakers-5817730%5C%22%3EBJP%20fails%20to%20reach%20the%20majority%20mark%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20its%20own%2C%20it%20will%20be%20pertinent%20to%20analyse%20what%20led%20to%20this%20situation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%2010%20Years%20Of%20Anti-Incumbency%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20have%20been%20saying%20from%20the%20beginning%2C%2010%20years%20of%20anti-incumbency%20may%20have%20damaged%20the%20BJP%20government's%20performance%20in%20the%20elections.%20The%20Modi%20government%20also%20refused%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20three%20issues%20that%20have%20made%20an%20ordinary%20citizen's%20life%20difficult%3A%20price%20rise%2C%20unemployment%20and%20corruption.%20The%20first%20two%20figured%20in%20every%20opinion%20poll%20as%20top%20issues%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20government%20failed%20to%20take%20enough%20remedial%20steps.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Top-Down%20Approach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20the%20BJP%20witness%20an%20erosion%20of%20seats%20in%20key%20battleground%20states%20because%20of%20the%20perceived%20top-down%20approach%3F%20Let%20us%20not%20forget%20that%20Indian%20civilisation%20puts%20a%20premium%20on%20values%20like%20humility%20and%20showing%20tolerance%20and%20respect%20to%20even%20adversaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Victory%20Taken%20For%20Granted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20consecration%2C%20the%20BJP%20perhaps%20took%20victory%20for%20granted.%20It%20is%20true%20that%20at%20the%20time%2C%20many%20in%20the%20opposition%20were%20also%20so%20demoralised%20that%20some%20in%20hushed%20tones%20admitted%20that%20the%20elections%20would%20be%20a%20cakewalk%20for%20the%20ruling%20party.%20It%20is%20also%20true%20that%20the%20enthusiasm%20around%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20was%20total%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20in%20a%20way%20could%20not%20gauge%20that%20this%20fervour%20would%20not%20automatically%20translate%20into%20votes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanalysis-chandrababu-naidu-makes-a-spectacular-comeback-after-jail-5814320%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Analysis%3A%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20Makes%20Spectacular%20Comeback%20After%20Jail%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20The%20Hyper-Focus%20On%20Congress%20Manifesto%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20it%20can%20be%20argued%20now%2C%20perhaps%20committed%20a%20blunder%20by%20reacting%20so%20aggressively%20to%20the%20Congress%20manifesto%20and%20comparing%20it%20to%20Muhammad%20Ali%20Jinnah's%20Muslim%20League%20manifesto%20of%201935.%20The%20attack%20inadvertently%20brought%20the%20Congress%20document%20centre%20stage%20and%20made%20it%20the%20talk%20of%20the%20town.%20After%20a%20long%20time%2C%20it%20was%20the%20Congress%20that%20was%20setting%20the%20agenda%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20reacting%20to%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20The%20Constitution%20Row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20never%20expected%20that%20the%20slogan%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3E400%20paar%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20would%20boomerang%20like%20this.%20Statements%20by%20leaders%20like%20Anant%20Hegde%2C%20that%20the%20BJP%20needed%20400%20seats%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution%2C%20angered%20Dalits%20and%20backward%20classes%20and%20instilled%20a%20fear%20that%20the%20party%20would%20take%20away%20their%20constitutional%20rights%20and%20privileges.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20silent%20but%20strong%20reaction%20from%20these%20sections.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20other%20INDIA%20leaders%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20carried%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20waved%20it%20in%20rallies%2C%20banking%20on%20that%20sentiment.%20Let's%20not%20forget%20that%20Dalits%20identify%20deeply%20with%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20and%20the%20debate%20around%20it%20seemed%20to%20them%20like%20an%20assault%20on%20Ambedkar's%20legacy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Fears%20Around%20Reservation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20linked%20the%20Constitution%20debate%20to%20reservations%2C%20and%20it%20turned%20into%20a%20discussion%20about%20how%20the%20BJP%20might%20take%20away%20reservations%20given%20to%20SCs%2C%20STs%20and%20OBCs%20if%20it%20came%20back%20to%20power.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20constantly%20hammered%20on%20the%20issue%20and%20it%20appears%20that%20this%20might%20have%20caught%20the%20imagination%20of%20these%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20The%20Waning%20Appeal%20Of%20A%20Hindu-Muslim%20Rhetoric%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20tried%20to%20polarise%20voters%20on%20communal%20lines%2C%20but%20the%20anti-Muslim%20rhetoric%20did%20not%20resonate%20well%20with%20voters.%20As%20a%20CSDS%20survey%20during%20the%20elections%20indicated%2C%20voters%20were%20largely%20growing%20weary%20of%20the%20Hindu-Muslim%20binary.%20Only%20for%202%25%20of%20respondents%20Hindutva%20was%20an%20election%20issue%2C%20while%20more%20than%2050%25%20believed%20that%20India%20is%20a%20plural%20society%20and%20it%20should%20remain%20so.%20This%20election%20has%20underlined%20the%20limits%20of%20Hindutva%20as%20well%20as%20the%20fact%20that%20communal%20polarisation%20can't%20be%20exploited%20beyond%20a%20point%20if%20economic%20delivery%20is%20poor.%20This%20election%20has%20also%20shown%20that%20the%20more%20Muslims%20were%20attacked%2C%20the%20more%20determined%20they%20were%20to%20vote%20unitedly%20against%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%20A%20Determined%20Opposition%20Front%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tenacity%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20another%20important%20factor.%20Opposition%20leaders%2C%20despite%20being%20on%20a%20weak%20wicket%2C%20continued%20their%20attacks%20and%20did%20not%20let%20the%20BJP%20successfully%20weave%20its%20own%20narrative.%20This%20was%20perhaps%20the%20ruling%20party's%20biggest%20failure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E9.%20The%20Arrival%20Of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20very%20serious%20contender%20in%20this%20election.%20His%20two%20Bharat%20Jodo%20%3Cem%3Eyatras%20%3C%2Fem%3Edid%20wonders%2C%20bestowing%20credibility%20on%20both%20Congress%20and%20Rahul.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnFinally%2C%20a%20question%20that%20must%20be%20asked%20is%2C%20why%20didn't%20free%20ration%20to%2080%20crore%20not%20help%20the%20BJP%20get%20272%20seats%3F%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnEvery%20election%20is%20different.%20The%20BJP%20may%20still%20form%20the%20government%2C%20but%20the%20aura%20of%20party's%20electoral%20invincibility%20stands%20dented.%20All%20this%20might%20lead%20to%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20politics%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%20Interesting%20times%20ahead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ashutosh%20is%20the%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20co-founder%20of%C2%A0SatyaHindi.com)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717566540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-02%2F801puc3k_pm-modi-rally-650_625x300_10_February_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Felection-result-2024-nine-things-that-may-explain-the-2024-mandate-5821774%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Did%20the%20BJP%20misread%20the%20situation%2C%20or%20did%20it%20refuse%20to%20read%20the%20writing%20on%20the%20wall%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Felection-result-2024-nine-things-that-may-explain-the-2024-mandate-5821774%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22WWDC%202024%3A%20Apple's%20iOS%2018%20first%20beta%20could%20bring%20these%20features%20to%20iPhones%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717566455000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-06%2F05%2Fthumb%2Ffacecrop%2F400X400%2F1717566223-8117.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fwwdc-2024-apple-s-ios-18-first-beta-could-bring-these-features-to-iphones-124060500319_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%20is%20anticipated%20to%20roll%20out%20iOS%2018%20soon%20after%20WWDC's%20keynote.%20The%20next-generation%20iPhone%20platform%20is%20expected%20to%20focus%20on%20AI%20integration%20within%20native%20apps%20and%20new%20interface%20design%20elements%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fwwdc-2024-apple-s-ios-18-first-beta-could-bring-these-features-to-iphones-124060500319_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fwwdc-2024-apple-s-ios-18-first-beta-could-bring-these-features-to-iphones-124060500319_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fwwdc-2024-apple-s-ios-18-first-beta-could-bring-these-features-to-iphones-124060500319_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bill%20Gates%2C%20Warren%20Buffett%20Have%20McDonald's%20Gold%20Card%20That%20Offers%20Free%20Food%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBill%20Gates%20and%20Warren%20Buffett%2C%20among%20the%20richest%20men%20in%20the%20world%2C%20have%20a%20special%20pass%20from%20McDonald's%20that%20offers%20them%20free%20meals.%20The%20Gold%20Card%20grants%20free%20food%20at%20all%20McDonald's%20outlets%20across%20the%20world%20for%20life%2C%20along%20with%20exclusive%20merchandise%20and%20food%20deals.%20According%20to%20latest%20update%20on%20the%20fat%20food%20giant's%20website%2C%20the%20Gold%20Card%20is%20based%20on%20two%20meals%20per%20week%20for%2050%20years.%20Mr%20Gates%20and%20Mr%20Buffett%2C%20both%20billionaires%2C%20revealed%20their%20Gold%20Card%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mr%20Buffett's%20Gold%20Card%20offers%20him%20eat%20for%20free%20at%20McDonald's%20outlets%20in%20Omaha%2C%20the%20one%20Mr%20Gates%20owns%20gives%20him%20free%20access%20to%20food%20at%20any%20McDonald's%20outlet%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Buffett%20displayed%20his%20Gold%20Card%20during%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2007%2F10%2F29%2Fwhats-in-warren-buffetts-wallet.html%5C%22%3Einterview%20with%20%3Cem%3ECNBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202007%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20explained%20how%20he%20uses%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20ah%2C%20here%20we%20have%20my%20McDonald's%20card%20which%20lets%20me%20eat%20free%20at%20any%20McDonald's%20in%20Omaha%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life.%20So%20that's%20why%20the%20Buffett%20family%20has%20Christmas%20dinner%20at%20McDonald's.%20It%20explains%20a%20lot%20of%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20chairperson%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20Mr%20Gates'%20card%20can%20be%20used%20worldwide.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20just%20a%20few%20of%20them.%20Bill%20Gates%20has%20one.%20His%20is%20good%20throughout%20the%20world%2C%20I%20guess.%20Mine%20is%20only%20good%20in%20Omaha%2C%20but%20I%20never%20leave%20Omaha%20so%20mine%20is%20just%20as%20good%20as%20his%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Buffett%2C%20then%2076%2C%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Buffett%20is%20the%20world's%20sixth%20richest%20person%20with%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%24134.9%20billion%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fprofile%2Fwarren-buffett%2F%3Fsh%3D15da6e064639%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gates%20too%20had%20mentioned%20about%20his%20Gold%20Card%20in%20an%20annual%20letter%20posted%20on%20his%20blog%20in%202017.%20The%20Microsoft%20co-founder%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3BRemember%20the%20laugh%20we%20had%20when%20we%20travelled%20together%20to%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20decided%20to%20get%20lunch%20at%20McDonald's%3F%20You%20offered%20to%20pay%2C%20dug%20into%20your%20pocket%20and%20pulled%20out%20coupons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20has%20not%20revealed%20the%20exact%20numbers%20of%20Gold%20Card%20holders%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717566300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fd999uqv_bill-gates-and-warren-buffett_625x300_05_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbill-gates-and-warren-buffett-have-mcdonalds-gold-card-that-offers-free-food-for-life-5821790%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22McDonald's%20has%20not%20revealed%20the%20exact%20numbers%20of%20Gold%20Card%20holders%20across%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbill-gates-and-warren-buffet