of%20India%20for%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20he%20extended%20his%20tenure%20by%20another%20potential%20five%20years%20when%20his%20ruling%20party%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20secured%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20lower%20house%20of%20parliament%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findia-election-results-narendra-modi-bjp-congress-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20key%20to%20everything%20being%20said%20about%20the%20world's%20biggest%20election%20%E2%80%94%20without%20his%20allies%2C%20Modi%20would%20have%20lost%20control%20of%20parliament%20and%2C%20by%20extension%2C%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20why%20the%20election%20results%20have%20been%20a%20shocking%20blow%20to%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20despite%20them%20winning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnyone%20seeking%20a%20majority%20in%20India's%20parliament%20%E2%80%94%20the%20prerequisite%20for%20naming%20a%20prime%20minister%20%E2%80%94%20needed%20to%20win%20272%20out%20of%20543%20seats.%20And%20this%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20only%20240%2C%20relying%20on%20smaller%20parties%20under%20a%20coalition%20called%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20to%20carry%20it%20past%20the%20finish%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20BJP%20that%20previously%20enjoyed%20a%20majority%20on%20its%20own%20with%20303%20seats%20in%202019%2C%20that's%20a%20stark%20shift%20in%20its%20grip%20on%20power.%20Its%20alliance%20only%20managed%20to%20secure%20293%20seats%2C%20just%2021%20more%20than%20needed%20for%20a%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20was%20especially%20humbling%20for%20Modi%20because%20the%20NDA%20was%20projected%20to%20slam-dunk%20the%20election%20with%20a%20whopping%20400%20seats.%20The%20incumbent%20seemed%20so%20confident%20that%20he%20declared%20victory%20three%20days%20before%20the%20result%20announcements%2C%20saying%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1796910902983450823%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20his%20voters%20turned%20out%20in%20%26quot%3Brecord%20numbers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20though%2C%20his%20allies%20hold%20the%20enviable%20position%20of%20being%20the%20difference-maker%20in%20deciding%20who%20leads%20India.%20Should%20they%20all%20ditch%20Modi%20for%20his%20rivals%20in%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%2C%20they%20could%20oust%20him%20from%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20biggest%20players%20in%20that%20gaggle%20of%20kingmakers%2C%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20and%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20hold%20a%20combined%2028%20seats%20and%20are%20led%20by%20politicians%20known%20for%20switching%20loyalties%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-06-04%2Fhere-are-the-india-kingmakers-who-will-determine-modi-s-future%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EModi%20now%20must%20ensure%20his%20coalition%20holds%20so%20he%20can%20remain%20in%20office%2C%20and%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-06-05%2Fmodi-seeks-to-shore-up-coalition-to-secure-third-term-in-power%3Fsrnd%3Dhomepage-asia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eset%20to%20enter%20talks%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20allied%20leaders%20to%20secure%20their%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20weakened%20hold%20on%20India's%20parliament%20was%20big%20news%20to%20observers%20concerned%20about%20the%20rise%20of%20his%20ideology%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fthe-economist-explains%2F2024%2F03%2F07%2Fwhat-is-hindutva-the-ideology-of-indias-ruling-party%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHindutva%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20promotes%20building%20a%20Hindu%20nation%20and%20has%20been%20criticized%20as%20right-wing%20and%20anti-Muslim%20extremism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227046a70a-a5bf-475f-8bc3-8b85cd3edb40%5C%22%3ESo%20why%20d