on%20in%20New%20York%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20opener%20against%20Ireland.%20As%20a%20fan%20breached%20security%20to%20meet%20Rohit%2C%20he%20was%20caught%20by%20officials%20at%20the%20ground%2C%20prompting%20Rohit%20to%20even%20suggest%20that%20the%20intruder%20should%20be%20dealt%20with%20a%20little%20easily.%20During%20the%20pre-match%20press%20conference%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Rohit%20was%20even%20asked%20about%20the%20incident%20by%20a%20reporter%2C%20but%20the%20Indian%20captain%20wasn't%20happy%20to%20be%20put%20under%20the%20spotlight%20for%20this%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20ahead%20of%20India's%20match%20against%20Ireland%2C%20Rohit%20was%20asked%20by%20a%20reporter%3A%20%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20warm%20up%20game%2C%20a%20fan%20had%20suddenly%20come%20on%20the%20ground.%20The%20way%20the%20security%20caught%20him%2C%20you%20were%20requesting%20him%20to%20take%20it%20easy.%20Can%20you%20tell%20us%20about%20the%20emotion%20at%20that%20time%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20was%20visibly%20disappointed%20at%20the%20question%20and%20said%20that%20both%20the%20incident%20and%20the%20question%20were%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSabse%20pahle%20toh%20main%20bolunga%20ki%20koi%20bhi%20aise%20ground%20mein%20intrude%20na%20kare.%20Ye%20sahi%20nahi%20hai%20aur%20yeh%20sawal%20bhi%20sahi%20nahi%20thha%20(See%2C%20first%20of%20all%2C%20I%20would%20say%20that%20no%20one%20should%20intrude%20into%20the%20ground.%20This%20is%20not%20right.%20And%20this%20question%20was%20also%20not%20right%2C%20because%20we%20don't%20want%20to%20promote%20this%20thing%20that%20who%20is%20running%20and%20coming%20to%20the%20ground)%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20captain%20further%20stressed%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20players'%20security%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20spectators.%20For%20this%20to%20happen%2C%20certain%20rules%20have%20to%20be%20followed%2C%20Rohit%20asserted.%3C%2F