0Mishra%20Teni%2C%20among%20others%2C%20were%20unseated%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-results-2024-smriti-irani-to-rajeev-chandrasekhar-union-ministers-who-lost-2024-polls-5821002%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-results-2024-smriti-irani-to-rajeev-chandrasekhar-union-ministers-who-lost-2024-polls-5821002%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-results-2024-smriti-irani-to-rajeev-chandrasekhar-union-ministers-who-lost-2024-polls-5821002%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Analysis%3A%2013%20Reasons%20Why%20Jagan%20Reddy%20Lost%20In%20Andhra%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOutgoing%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20says%20he%20does%20not%20know%20the%20reason%20why%20despite%20bringing%20welfare%20to%20maximum%20households%2C%20the%20elderly%2C%20women%2C%20farmers%2C%20auto%20drivers%20and%20others%2C%20he%20and%20his%20party%2C%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20had%20faced%20such%20a%20humiliating%20defeat%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YSRCP%20had%20won%20151%20assembly%20and%2023%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20with%20nearly%2050%20per%20cent%20vote%20share%20in%202019.%20Going%20down%20to%2040%20per%20cent%20vote%20share%20in%202024%20has%20left%20the%20party%20with%20just%2010%20assembly%20and%20four%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%2013%20possible%20reasons%20why%20Jagan%20Mohan%C2%A0Reddy%20and%20his%20party%20performed%20badly%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20%C2%A0%20Arrest%20of%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20in%20September%2C%202023%2C%20shocked%20his%20admirers%20and%20supporters%20specially%20among%20the%20educated%20class%20who%20considered%20Mr%20Naidu%20as%20an%20icon%20of%20progressive%20Telugu%20political%20leadership.%20The%20police%20action%20was%20suspected%20to%20be%20vendetta%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrest%20of%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20may%20not%20have%20directly%20translated%20into%20a%20sympathy%20wave%20but%20Mr%20Naidu%20was%20a%20tall%20leader%20who%20had%20many%20admirers.%20For%20a%20senior%2C%20much-respected%20politician%20to%20be%20put%20behind%20bars%2C%20reeked%20of%20a%20vengeful%20government%20out%20to%20settle%20scores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20%C2%A0%20The%20turning%20point%20in%20changing%20the%20fortunes%20of%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20Telugu%20Desam%20came%20with%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20playing%20the%20hero%20for%20a%20party%20in%20distress%20and%20announcing%20that%20he%20and%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20would%20fight%20the%20election%20along%20with%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20the%20TDP.%20Post%20the%20arrest%2C%20the%20CBN%20camp%20had%20appeared%20in%20low%20spirits%20and%20were%20not%20looking%20quite%20capable%20of%20spinning%20a%20political%20comeback.%20But%20the%20star's%20entry%20and%20standing%20with%20Mr%20Lokesh%20outside%20Rajahmundry%20Central%20Prison%20served%20as%20a%20powerful%20image%20that%20boosted%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20cadres%2C%20and%20even%20the%20people%2C%20that%20Naidu%20could%20be%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20%C2%A0%20Lessons%20from%20Telangana%20and%20KCR%20did%20not%20help%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20and%20the%20YSRCP%3A%20If%20the%20BRS%20had%20lost%20the%202023%20assembly%20election%20because%20KCR%20did%20not%20change%20candidates%2C%20YS%20Jaganmohan%20Reddy%20changed%20some%20102%20candidates%20but%20that%20did%20not%20pay%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20%C2%A0%20The%20poll%20arithmetic%20of%20the%20NDA%20alliance%20worked%20perfectly%2C%20with%20the%20vote%20share%20apparently%20happening%20smoothly%20between%20the%20alliance%20partners.%20Mr%20Naidu%20and%20Mr%20Kalyan%20ensured%20they%20met%20regularly%2C%20courteously%20and%20put%20up%20a%20chemistry%20in%20their%20appearances%20together%20that%20gave%20the%20right%20signals%20to%20the%20party%20cadre.%20No%20dirty%20linen%20was%20ever%20washed%20in%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20The%20volunteer%20system%20to%20reach%20governance%20and%20administration%20to%20the%20doorstep%20of%20the%20most%20deprived%20sections%20worked%20well.%20But%20the%20official%20machinery%20got%20neglected.%20That%20created%20resentment%20and%20the%20political%20parties%20were%20not%20able%20to%20build%20their%20popularity%20on%20a%20patronage%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20more%20important%20is%20the%20fear%20factor%20that%20critics%20talk%20about.%20Fear%20of%20being%20identified%20as%20a%20TDP%20supporter%20and%20getting%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20%C2%A0%20The%20narrative%20that%20the%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20government%20did%20not%20focus%20on%20anything%20beyond%20welfare%20measures%20had%20a%20resonance%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20There%20was%20talk%20of%20the%20elderly%20and%20the%20women%2C%20who%20have%20been%20beneficiaries%2C%20being%20pressured%20by%20the%20youth%20who%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3Bokay%2C%20you%20are%20getting%20money%20in%20your%20pocket%2C%20but%20what%20about%20our%20future%2C%20our%20jobs%3F%26quot%3B%2C%20convincing%20a%20change%20in%20party%20loyalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0Mr%20Naidu%2C%20Mr%20Kalyan%20and%20Mr%20Lokesh%20repeatedly%20called%20Mr%20Reddy%20a%20psycho.%20They%20asked%20the%20question%3A%20who%20killed%20babai%3F%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20murder%20of%20Mr%20Reddy's%C2%A0uncle%20YS%20Vivekananda%20Reddy%2C%20creating%20doubt%20and%20suspicion%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYS%20Sharmila%20has%20not%20won%20Kadapa.%20Yet%20her%20campaign%2C%20targetting%20her%20brother%2C%20as%20someone%20who%20is%20supporting%20the%20murder%20accused%20of%20their%20uncle%2C%20did%20not%20help%20Mr%20Reddy's%20image%20among%20the%20people.%20Afterall%2C%20Ms%20Sharmila%20had%20campaigned%20for%20Mr%20Reddy%2C%20even%20undertook%20a%20padyatra%20for%20him.%20Yet%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20she%20was%20not%20just%20estranged%20but%20had%20gone%20against%20him%20publicly%2C%20led%20to%20gossip%20about%20palace%20intrigue%20and%20of%20greed%2C%20avarice%2C%20little%20value%20for%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8.%20%C2%A0%20Just%20like%20in%20Telangana%2C%20there%20was%20also%20talk%20of%20Mr%20Reddy%20getting%20surrounded%20by%20a%20coterie%20that%20did%20not%20allow%20genuine%20feedback%20to%20reach%20him.%20Even%20though%20he%20came%20across%20as%20a%20people's%20man%20in%20his%20political%20yatras%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20is%20not%20known%20to%20be%20gregarious%20and%20liked%20his%20personal%20space%20and%20time%20with%20his%20family%20and%20that%20did%20lead%20to%20resentment%20about%20no%20access.%20Like%20KCR%2C%20he%20too%20got%20labelled%20authoritarian%20and%20inaccessible.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn9.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0The%20sheer%20power%20of%20numbers%3A%20As%20against%20YS%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20who%20came%20across%20as%20a%20singular%20face%2C%20a%20lone%20soldier%20and%20campaigner%20for%20his%20party%2C%20the%20NDA%20had%20many%2C%20many%20faces.%20From%20a%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20to%20a%20Pawan%20Kalyan%2C%20both%20of%20who%20campaigned%20extensively%20and%20as%20though%20there%20was%20no%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlus%20the%20momentum%20of%20a%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Home%20Minister%20and%20other%20BJP%20leaders%20adding%20voice%20and%20volume%20to%20the%20NDA%20campaign%2C%20gave%20it%20a%20momentum%20that%20YSRCP%20was%20not%20able%20to%20match.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10.%20Already%20Nara%20Lokesh%20had%20undertaken%20a%203132%20km%20over%20226%20days%2C%20called%20Yuvagalam%2C%20that%20helped%20the%20younger%20TDP%20leader%20connect%20directly%20with%20the%20people%2C%20like%20Mr%20Reddy%20had%20done%20earlier.%20Mr%20Lokesh%20walked%20from%20Kuppam%20in%20southern%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20to%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20taking%20a%20break%20only%20when%20his%20father%20went%20to%20jail.%20He%20listened%20to%20people's%20grievances%2C%20promising%20to%20address%20them%20when%20the%20TDP%20came%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E11.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20took%20no%20chances%20and%20presented%20a%20manifesto%20that%20included%20Mr%20Reddy's%20welfare%20promises%20and%20more.%20The%20man%20once%20known%20for%20economic%20reforms%20now%20was%20proposing%20a%20manifesto%20that%20was%20clearly%20financially%20unviable%20for%20a%20state%20without%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A012.%20The%20campaign%20around%20the%20Land%20Titling%20Act%20was%20probably%20the%20last%20nail%20on%20the%20coffin.%20It%20created%20doubts%20and%20apprehension%20around%20not%20just%20selling%20and%20buying%20land%20but%20also%20about%20losing%20your%20land%2C%20not%20being%20able%20to%20either%20inherit%20land%20or%20pass%20it%20on%20to%20your%20children.%20The%20YSRCP%20was%20not%20able%20to%20do%20enough%20damage%20control%20in%20time%20and%20that%20possibly%20nailed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E13.%20Finally%2C%20no%20ruling%20party%20can%20afford%20to%20underestimate%20the%20power%20of%20its%20employees.%20The%20attack%20on%20doctors%2C%20unhappiness%20of%20teachers%2C%20action%20on%20anganwadi%20workers%20and%20resentment%20among%20the%208%20lakh%20government%20employees%20about%20denial%20or%20delay%20in%20pay%20out%20of%20benefits%2C%20had%20for%20some%20time%20now%20metamorphed%20into%20whispers%20in%20the%20corridors%20of%20power%20that%20this%20government%20must%20be%20voted%20out.%20That%20probably%20sealed%20the%20YSRCP%20fate.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717558860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F6ugrnj2k_jagan-reddy-1200-_625x300_30_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fandhra-pradesh-news%2Fanalysis-13-reasons-why-jagan-mohan-reddy-lost-in-andhra-pradesh-5818630%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Outgoing%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Jagan%20Mo