%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Finterpol-fbi-and-nca-thwart-criminal-gang-trying-to-sabotage-red-notice-system-13148089%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Finterpol-fbi-and-nca-thwart-criminal-gang-trying-to-sabotage-red-notice-system-13148089%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Finterpol-fbi-and-nca-thwart-criminal-gang-trying-to-sabotage-red-notice-system-13148089%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supriya%20Sule%20Defeats%20Sister-In-Law%20In%20Baramati%20Prestige%20Battle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOvercoming%20the%20challenge%20posed%20by%20her%20estranged%20cousin%2C%20NCP%20(SP)%20candidate%20Supriya%20Sule%20on%20Tuesday%20retained%20her%20Baramati%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20by%20more%20than%201.55%20lakh%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sule%20triumphed%20over%20her%20sister-in-law%20Sunetra%20Pawar%2C%20wife%20of%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20a%20political%20debutante%2C%20in%20the%20battle%20that%20had%20become%20the%20most%20high-profile%20contest%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sule%20polled%207%2C32%2C312%20votes%20while%20Sunetra%20Pawar%20garnered%205%2C73%2C979%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar%2C%20Ms%20Sule's%20cousin%20who%20rebelled%20against%20her%20father%20Sharad%20Pawar%20last%20year%20and%20split%20the%20party%2C%20is%20known%20to%20enjoy%20a%20lot%20of%20support%20in%20the%20family%20bastion%20of%20Baramati%2C%20and%20hence%2C%20many%20political%20observers%20felt%20that%20Ms%20Sule%20would%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20win%20the%20fourth%20consecutive%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20his%20wife's%20defeat%20would%20be%20a%20major%20setback.%20His%20son%20Parth%20Pawar%20had%20lost%20as%20the%20candidate%20of%20the%20undivided%20NCP%20from%20the%20Maval%20constituency%20in%20the%202019%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high-octane%20contest%20in%20Baramati%20t