t%2C%20I%20know%20the%20mentality%20of%20the%20common%20voters%20here%2C%20as%20they%20take%20the%20right%20call%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717557360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fs60agem_supriya-sule_625x300_13_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-results-supriya-sule-defeats-ajit-pawar-wife-sunetra-pawar-retains-baramati-seat-for-4th-time-5820907%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Overcoming%20the%20challenge%20posed%20by%20her%20estranged%20cousin%2C%20NCP%20(SP)%20candidate%20Supriya%20Sule%20on%20Tuesday%20retained%20her%20Baramati%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20by%20more%20than%201.55%20lakh%20votes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-results-supriya-sule-defeats-ajit-pawar-wife-sunetra-pawar-retains-baramati-seat-for-4th-time-5820907%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-results-supriya-sule-defeats-ajit-pawar-wife-sunetra-pawar-retains-baramati-seat-for-4th-time-5820907%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-results-supriya-sule-defeats-ajit-pawar-wife-sunetra-pawar-retains-baramati-seat-for-4th-time-5820907%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cillian%20Murphy%3A%20Peaky%20Blinders%20film%20is%20for%20the%20fans%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717557171000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110718282%2Cimgsize-53440.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fcillian-murphy-returns-as-tommy-shelby