ay%20culture%20which%20is%20common%20in%20China%2C%20Korea%2C%20and%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20podcast%20'Invest%20Aaj%20For%20Kal%20with%20Anant%20Ladha'%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%2084-hour%20work%20week%20would%20%26quot%3Baccelerate%20the%20country's%20growth%26quot%3B%20and%20will%20help%20people%20to%20transfer%20to%20%26quot%3Bmiddle%20and%20upper-income%20levels%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20clip%2C%20going%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCharlie%20Munger%20wrote%20in%20one%20of%20his%20books%20that%20people%20in%20Korea%20worked%2084%20hours%20a%20week%20for%20one%20generation.%20That%20means%2012%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20every%20day%2C%20every%20month%2C%20every%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWe%20need%20to%20work%2012%20hours%20per%20day%20for%20365%20days%20-%20Nilesh%20Shah%20sir%20-%20CE0%20Kotak%20AMC%20%F0%9F%91%87%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FtiXQSgwT5r%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FtiXQSgwT5r%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Anant%20Ladha%2C%20CFA%20CA%20CFP%20LL.B.%20(%40anantladha25)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fanantladha25%2Fstatus%2F1796751172210139278%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%201%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BRecently%20in%20India%2C%20Narayana%20Murthy%20mentioned%20working%2070%20hours%20a%20week%2C%20which%20created%20a%20controversy.%20He%20said%20that%20Indians%20need%20to%20work%20like%20Koreans%2C%20Chinese%2C%20and%20Japanese.%20If%20we%20work%20hard%2C%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20India's%20growth%20will%20continue%2C%20the%20pace%20will%20accelerate%2C%20and%20there%20will%20come%20a%20time%20when%20there%20will%20be%20no%20sub-Saharan%20Africa-level%20poverty%20in%20India.%20We%20will%20have%20transferred%20e