%20partially%20empty%20and%20isolated.%20However%2C%20India%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20hopeful%20to%20see%20the%20fans%20turn%20up%20for%20their%20group%20games.%20India%20will%20play%20three%20of%20their%20four%20group%20games%20in%20New%20York%20against%20Ireland%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20USA%2C%20while%20their%20last%20league%20game%20against%20Canada%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20slightly%20different%20and%20exciting%20to%20have%20a%20World%20Cup%20coming%20to%20a%20new%20country%2C%20and%20a%20new%20place.%20Things%20are%20very%20different%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20buzz%2C%20as%20cricket%20is%20not%20one%20of%20the%20major%20sports%20in%20the%20country.%20Hopefully%2C%20when%20our%20games%20come%20in%2C%20the%20Indian%20fans%20start%20to%20come%20in%20and%20bring%20that%20similar%20kind%20of%20excitement%2C%26quot%3B%20Dravid%20said%20in%20a%20pre-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20team's%20arrival%20in%20the%20Big%20Apple%2C%20the%20Indian%20players%20have%20been%20training%20at%20the%20Cantiague%20Park%2C%20which%20is%20located%20in%20Hicksville.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20admitting%20that%20it's%20been%20a%20bit%20strange%20training%20in%20a%20public%20park%2C%20Dravid%20insisted%20that%20it%20has%20been%20an%20enjoybale%20experience%20to%20train%20at%20the%20Cantiague%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20in%20terms%20of%20what%20we%20wanted%20out%20of%20practice%2C%20it%20hasn't%20the%20way%20we%20practice%20or%20the%20professionalism%20we%20have%20in%20terms%20of%20approaching%20things%2C%20which%20is%20very%20much%20like%20what%20we%20do%20normally.%20It%20is%20a%20bit%20strange%20that%20we%20are%20practicing%20in%20the%20park%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20practicing%20in%20cricket%20stadiums%20during%20other%20ev