%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20try%20to%20understand%20the%20main%20takeaway%20of%20this%20election%3A%20how%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20lost%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20thereby%20its%20sole%20Lok%20Sabha%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20swung%20the%20national%20verdict%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20nobody%20anticipated%20that%2C%20let%20alone%20predict%20it.%20Nobody%20stuck%20her%20or%20his%20neck%20out%20and%20said%20the%20Congress-Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20alliance%20would%20win%20more%20seats%20than%20the%20BJP.%20Yogendra%20Yadav's%20phase-wise%20election%20overview%20and%20his%20heartfelt%20write-ups%20based%20on%20his%20travels%20through%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20zeroed%20in%20on%20the%20many%20factors%20that%20resulted%20in%20the%2019%25%20swing%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress-SP%20alliance%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%209%25%20vote%20drop%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%2010%25%20for%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP).%20Yadav%20was%20the%20closest%20anybody%20got%20to%20sensing%20the%20electorate%20earthquake%20that%2C%20single-handedly%2C%C2%A0%20prevented%20the%20BJP%20from%20getting%20a%20simple%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlind%20Men%20And%20A%20Rather%20Big%20Elephant%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20would%20argue%20that%20prominent%20YouTube%20channels%20in%20Hindi%2C%20most%20notably%20Red%20Mike%2C%20as%20well%20as%20innumerable%20bloggers%2C%20also%20gave%20glimpses%20of%20the%20surge%20in%20the%20Congress-SP%20support.%20Like%20that%20proverbial%20tale%20of%20the%20blind%20men%20and%20the%20elephant%2C%20many%20sharp%20observers%20correctly%20felt%20the%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20elephant%2C%20but%20nobody%20realised%20that%20it%20was%20an%20elephant%20-%20and%20a%20rather%20big%20one%20-%20they%20were%20facing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dalit%20vote%20was%20going%20to%20be%20critical%2C%20and%20it%20was%20correctly%20observed%20that%20the%20BJP's%20aligning%20of%20non-Jatavs%20against%20the%20BSP's%20Jatav%20base%20-%20one%20of%20the%20key%20tactical%20drivers%20of%20its%20sweep%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20last%20general%20as%20well%20as%20two%20assembly%20elections%20-%20had%20come%20undone%20over%20the%20Congress's%20charge%20that%20a%20%26quot%3B400%20paar%26quot%3B%20mandate%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20change%20in%20the%20Constitution.%20But%20nobody%20anticipated%20that%20Jatavs%2C%20whose%2013%25%20vote%20share%20dominates%20the%20Dalit%20base%2C%20would%20also%20vote%20tactically%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20that%20to%20happen%2C%20the%20Jatavs%20had%20not%20only%20to%20jettison%20the%20BSP%20but%20also%20get%20over%20their%20antipathy%20towards%20the%20Yadav-dominated%20SP.%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Dalits%20have%20long%20regarded%20the%20Yadavs%20as%20their%20worst%20oppressors%3B%20memories%20are%20still%20fresh%20of%20the%20law%20and%20order%20mayhem%20under%20the%20SP%20regime%20before%20Yogi%20Adityanath.%20Dalits%2C%20especially%20Jatavs%2C%20have%20not%20forgotten%20the%20Lucknow%20%26quot%3BGuest%20House%26quot%3B%20incident%20of%201995%2C%20when%20aggressive%20SP%20legislators%20and%20supporters%20came%20close%20to%20physically%20molesting%20Mayawati.%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20carried%20that%20cross%20as%20long%20as%20he%20was%20alive.%20The%20SP-BSP%20alliance%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20did%20little%20to%20heal%20the%20emotional%20scar%2C%20even%20if%20it%20fetched%2016%20seats.%20But%20it%20was%20still%20wholly%20unexpected%20that%20'Behenji's'%20Jatav%20vote%20would%20abandon%20her%20in%20such%20totality%20when%20it%20became%20evident%20that%20her%20ticket%20selection%20for%20the%20BSP%20was%20clearly%20aimed%20at%20improving%20the%20BJP's%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAkhilesh's%20Deft%20Social%20Engineering%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObservers%20also%20noted%20that%20this%20time%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20ticket%20distribution%20indicated%20much%20smarter%20social%20engineering%20as%20it%20marked%20a%20departure%20from%20the%20party's%20almost%20total%20reliance%20on%20its%20Muslim-Yadav%20(MY)%20base.%20Tickets%20were%20given%20to%20only%20nine%20MY%20candidates%3A%20five%20Yadavs%2C%20all%20relatives%20of%20Akhilesh%2C%20and%20four%20Muslims.%20The%20rest%20of%20its%2048%20candidates%20were%20drawn%20mainly%20from%20the%20myriad%20other%20OBCs%2C%20denting%20another%20pillar%20of%20Amit%20Shah's%20social%20engineering%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20he%20had%20won%20over%20the%20non-Yadavs%20by%20pitting%20them%20against%20the%20Yadavs.%20There%20were%20a%20couple%20of%20other%20counter-intuitive%20choices%20too%20by%20Akhilesh%3A%20a%20ticket%20to%20a%20feisty%20Jatav%20woman%20in%20Meerut%20(a%20general%20seat)%2C%20and%20another%20to%20a%20Brahmin%20in%20Ballia%2C%20where%20Rajputs%20have%20long%20reigned%20and%20where%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20was%20the%20son%20of%20arguably%20one%20of%20the%20tallest%20Rajput%20leader%2C%20ex-Prime%20Minister%20and%20veteran%20Congressman%2C%20Chandra%20Shekhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20also%20noted%20the%20restiveness%20among%20the%20Jats%20in%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20But%20it%20was%20believed%20that%20the%20BJP's%20alliance%20with%20Jayant%20Chaudhury%2C%20grandson%20of%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20and%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20(RLD)%20chief%2C%20would%20rally%20the%20Jats.%20Add%20to%20that%20the%20party's%20decades-old%20politics%20of%20polarisation%20in%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20-%20which%20successfully%20dented%20the%20Jat-Muslim%20base%20of%20Charan%20Singh's%20RLD%20-%20as%20well%20as%20its%20Hindutva%20support%20base%2C%20and%20many%20were%20sure%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20bring%20the%20bacon%20home%20in%20this%20part%20of%20the%20state%20given%20the%20significant%20Muslim%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMention%20was%20also%20made%20of%20the%20resentment%20among%20Rajputs%20over%20Yogi%20Adityanath's%20apparent%20sidelining%20in%20the%20seat-selection%20process%2C%20allegedly%20by%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20the%20most%20visible%20BJP%20leader%20after%20Modi.%20His%20188%20rallies%20across%20the%20country%20were%20seen%20as%20a%20pointer%20to%20the%20who-after-Modi%20question.%20The%20denial%20of%20tickets%20to%20a%20few%20good%20candidates%2C%20including%20General%20V.K.%20Singh%2C%20a%20Rajput%2C%20was%20also%20mentioned%20as%20a%20red%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Assessment%20Quite%20Off%20The%20Mark%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20the%20overall%20assessment%20had%20been%20that%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20and%20allies%20won%2064%20out%20of%2080%20seats%20in%20the%20previous%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20was%20well%20within%20its%20control.%20The%20party's%20popularity%20in%20the%20crucial%20and%20populous%20Doaba%20region%2C%20with%20Ayodhya%20as%20the%20epicentre%2C%20was%20never%20in%20doubt.%20When%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20forsook%20Amethi%2C%20it%20did%20seem%20that%20he%20was%20running%20away%20from%20the%20battlefield%2C%20sensing%20another%20defeat%20-%20something%20the%20BJP%20crowed%20about%20relentlessly.%20Meanwhile%2C%20there%20weren't%20too%20many%20doubts%20about%20the%20BJP's%20dominance%20in%20Bundelkhand%2C%20a%20region%20entwined%20with%20the%20party's%20stronghold%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20all%20this%2C%20as%20the%20seven-phase%20elections%20rolled%20across%20the%20state%20and%20headed%20to%20the%20Purvanchal%20region%20(or%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh)%2C%20trends%20emerged%20that%20ought%20to%20have%20triggered%20serious%20doubts.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20were%20forced%20to%20abandon%20an%20election%20meeting%20in%20Phulpur%2C%20near%20Allahabad%20(Prayagraj)%2C%20after%20a%20massive%20crowd%20erupted%20in%20enthusiasm%20and%20breached%20security%20barriers%20to%20greet%20them.%20This%20was%20well-noticed.%20Veteran%20journalist%20Neerja%20Chowdhury%2C%20who%20was%20present%20at%20the%20meeting%2C%20said%20in%20a%20podcast%20later%20that%20the%20fervour%20she%20saw%20among%20Congress-SP%20supporters%20reminded%20her%20of%20the%20excitement%20she%20witnessed%20in%201987-89%20when%20V.P.%20Singh%20was%20set%20to%20storm%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20fort%20on%20the%20back%20of%20his%20Bofors-charged%20challenge%20to%20Rajiv%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThrowback%20To%201977%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20association%2C%20if%20I%20may%20be%20allowed%20a%20personal%20detour%2C%20should%20have%20alerted%20me.%20I%20have%20covered%20numerous%20elections%20between%201977%20and%202014.%20Coincidentally%2C%20both%20those%20elections%20were%20'wave'%20elections%2C%20where%20the%20crowd%20support%20in%20meetings%20and%20rallies%20was%20so%20manifest%20that%20you%20needed%20to%20be%20blind%20to%20not%20see%20the%20winner.%20And%20yet%2C%20I%20have%20not%20seen%20the%20kind%20of%20fervour%20I%20experienced%20in%20Varanasi%20in%20one%20of%20V.P.%20Singh's%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3ERaja%20Nahi%20Fakir%20Hai%2C%20Desh%20Ki%20Takdeer%20Hai%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20rallies.%20I%20was%20in%20Singh's%20Jeep%2C%20merely%20an%20arm's%20distance%20from%20him%2C%20and%20I%20have%20not%20seen%20that%20kind%20of%20mania%20at%20any%20meeting%20ever%20-%20neither%20in%20the%20hugely%20emotional%20election%20rallies%20of%20any%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20in%201977%20nor%20in%20any%20of%20Modi's%20rallies%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20or%20Bihar%20in%202014.%20Balconies%20of%20the%20houses%20along%20the%20streets%20were%20packed%20and%20brimming%20as%20people%20showered%20flowers%20on%20their%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BRaja%20Sahib%26quot%3B.%20To%20be%20sure%2C%20these%20were%20not%20flowers%20supplied%20by%20Mr%20Singh's%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20nobody%20thought%20that%20any%20of%20this%20would%20push%20the%20Congress-SP%20vote%20and%20seat%20share%20past%20that%20of%20the%20BJP's.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI'm%20reminded%20again%20of%20a%20vignette%20from%20the%201977%20election.%20We%20were%20at%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Muzaffarpur%2C%20Northwestern%20Bihar%2C%20where%20the%20Janata%20Party%20candidate%2C%20George%20Fernandes%2C%20was%20fighting%20from%20jail.%20Madhu%20Limaye%2C%20a%20giant%20figure%20from%20the%20Socialist%20Party%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20main%20speakers.%20He%20noticed%20a%20few%20supporters%20getting%20boisterous%20as%20they%20shouted%20slogans%20hailing%20the%20leaders.%20He%20called%20out%20to%20them%20and%20said%20something%20to%20this%20effect%3A%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BItney%20nashey%20mein%20mat%20raho%3B%20agla%20election%20hum%20haar%20bhi%20saktey%20hain%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Don't%20jump%20around%2C%20we%20may%20lose%20the%20next%20election).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Waning%20Of%20The%20'Magic'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrashant%20Kishor%2C%20one%20of%20the%20more%20astute%20observers%20of%20Indian%20politics%2C%20explained%20in%20his%20TV%20interviews%20why%20he%20thought%20the%20BJP%20would%20end%20up%20near%20its%202019%20tally%20of%20303%20seats.%20Modi's%20popularity%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20the%20leitmotif%20of%20the%20party's%20dominance.%20This%20popularity%20rests%20on%20four%20pillars%3A%20Hindutva%2C%20alignment%20of%20nationalism%20with%20Hindutva%2C%20the%20improvement%20in%20the%20material%20life%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Elabharthis%3C%2Fem%3E%20through%20what%20has%20been%20termed%20%26quot%3Bnew%20welfarism%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20the%20BJP's%20stupendous%20organisational%20strength%20and%20resource%20superiority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20will%20continue%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20over%20which%20of%20these%20four%20pillars%20caved%20in%20and%20by%20how%20much.%20But%20one%20fact%20has%20been%20cemented%20yet%20again%3A%20there%20is%20a%20'sell-by'%20date%20for%20every%20product.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ajay%20Kumar%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist.%20He%20is%20former%20Managing%20Editor%2C%20Business%20Standard%2C%20and%20former%20Executive%20Editor%2C%20The%20Economic%20Times.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717549260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2F14i3r5do_rahul-gandhi-akhilesh-yadav_625x300_17_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-result-how-everyone-failed-to-read-the-tea-leaves-against-bjp-in-uttar-pradesh-5818762%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20debate%20will%20continue%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20over%20which%20of%20these%20four%20pillars%20caved%20in%20and%20by%20how%20much.%20But%20one%20fact%20has%20been%20cemented%20yet%20again%3A%20there%20is%20a%20'sell-by'%20date%20for%20every%20product.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-result-how-everyone-failed-to-read-the-tea-leaves-against-bjp-in-uttar-pradesh-5818762%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Details%20you%20might%20have%20missed%20in%20'Star%20Wars%3A%20The%20Acolyte'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223228%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Carrie-Anne%20Moss%20as%20Master%20Indara%20in%20%26quot%3BStar%20Wars%3A%20The%20Acolyte.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665deb231cd3b1779042911f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222421%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECarrie-Anne%20Moss%20as%20Master%20Indara%20in%20%26quot%3BStar%20Wars%3A%20The%20Acolyte.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EChristian%20Black%2FLucasfilm%2FDisney%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Acolyte%26quot%3B%20is%20set%20100%20years%20before%20%26quot%3BStar%20Wars%3A%20Episode%20I%20-%20The%20Phantom%20Menace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20follows%20a%20Jedi%20Master%20who%2