s%20left%2C%20though%20the%20company%20has%20since%20formed%20a%20new%20safety%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20past%20years%2C%20safety%20culture%20and%20processes%20have%20taken%20a%20backseat%20to%20shiny%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20Leike%20wrote%20in%20a%20series%20of%20social%20media%20posts%20around%20his%20departure.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20disagreeing%20with%20OpenAI%20leadership%20about%20the%20company's%20core%20priorities%20for%20quite%20some%20time%2C%20until%20we%20finally%20reached%20a%20breaking%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20concerns%20are%20heightened%20as%20the%20company%20approaches%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0or%20technology%20capable%20of%20all%20human%20behavior.%20Many%20experts%20say%20AGI%20increases%20the%20likelihood%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwill-ai-destroy-humanity-pdoom-ai-number-doomer-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ep(doom)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20nerdy%20and%20depressing%20term%20for%20the%20probability%20of%20AI%20destroying%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20put%20it%20bluntly%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-glory-days-ending-problems-chatgpt-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleading%20AI%20researcher%20Stuart%20Russell%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20to%20BI%20last%20month%3A%20%26quot%3BEven%20people%20who%20are%20developing%20the%20technology%20say%20there's%20a%20chance%20of%20human%20extinction.%20What%20gave%20them%20the%20right%20to%20play%20Russian%20roulette%20with%20everyone's%20children%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22757edae6-3d1d-45a9-b19b-54f28a7b9c5f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20A-list%20actor%20and%20NDAs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20probably%20didn't%20have%20it%20on%20your%202024%20bingo%20card%20that%20Black%20Widow%20would%20take%20on%20a%20Silicon%20Valley%20giant%2C%20but%20here%20we%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20