ams%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ice-candy%20and%20%3Cem%3Egola%20%3C%2Fem%3Econtinued%20well%20into%20his%20adulthood%2C%20and%20became%20%E2%80%98all-weather%20friends%E2%80%99%20for%20the%2037-year-old.%20He%20rose%20from%20being%20a%20team%20member%20at%20Pizza%20Hut%20to%20managing%20big%20brands%20like%20Gloria%20Jeans%20Coffee%20and%20Rasna%2C%20and%20now%20runs%20a%20successful%20ice-cream%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20youngest%20of%20four%20siblings%2C%20Gagan%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20middle-class%20home%20with%20lofty%20dreams%20of%20becoming%20an%20actor.%20However%2C%20his%20father%20retired%20when%20he%20had%20just%20completed%20Class%2010%2C%20which%20propelled%20him%20towards%20making%20his%20own%20life%20through%20sheer%20hard%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Rs%201%2C200%20in%20his%20pocket%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20New%20Delhi%20to%20pursue%20acting%20at%20just%2016.%20He%20soon%20realised%20that%20making%20a%20name%20for%20yourself%20in%20this%20field%20was%20rather%20difficult.%20Roaming%20around%20Connaught%20Place%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20doors%20of%20Pizza%20Hut%20beckoned%20him%20towards%20a%20more%20stable%20career%20path.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20as%20a%20part-time%20team%20member%20at%2017%20after%20completing%20his%20Class%2012%2C%20the%20ambitious%20young%20man%20rose%20through%20the%20ranks%20to%20become%20a%20restaurant%20general%20manager%20at%2021.%20From%20there%20on%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20international%20and%20Indian%20brands%20for%20over%2018%20years%20before%20deciding%20to%20build%20a%20company%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-03-at-18.45.33-min-1717420586-500x750.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gagan%20Anand%2C%20Founder%2C%20Scuzo%20Ice-O-Magic%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A