rds%20over%20the%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20name%20a%20few%2C%20in%202015%2C%20the%20foundation%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20British%20Medical%20Association%20South%20Asia%20Award%20for%20establishing%20a%20cadaver%20programme%20in%20India.%20In%202021%2C%20he%20was%20given%20the%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award%20from%20Grant%20Thornton%20Sabera.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Dr%20Shroff%20received%20the%20Dr%20K%20C%20G%20Verghese%C2%A0Excellence%C2%A0Awards%20for%20Community%20Service.%20The%20MOHAN%20Foundation%20also%20received%20the%20%E2%80%98Best%20NGO%20Award%E2%80%99%20in%202023%20from%20NOTTO%2C%20DGHS%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20National%20Organ%20Donation%20Day.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Sunil%20Shroff%20receiving%20Dr%20K%20C%20G%20Verghese%20Excellence%20Awards%202023.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-300x134.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-500x223.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-768x343.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-1536x687.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-2048x915.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-150x67.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351941%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221144%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Sunil%20Shroff%20receiving%20Dr%20K%20C%20G%20Verghese%20Excellence%20Awards%202023.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shroff%20is%20the%20Asia%20convenor%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Tribute%20to%20Life%20for%20Commonwealth%20Organ%20Donation%20Project%E2%80%99.%20He%20is%20primarily%20responsible%20for%20establishing%20the%20%E2%80%98Indian%20Organ%20Transplant%20Registry%E2%80%99%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Indian%20Society%20of%20Organ%20Transplantation.%20This%20registry%2C%20a%20first%20in%20Asia%2C%20has%20been%20crucial%20for%20compiling%20data%20on%20kidney%20transplants%20in%20India%20and%20analysing%20their%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shroff%20believes%20that%20Indians%20are%20very%20emotional%20people%3B%20very%20giving%20people.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20just%20some%20distrust%20with%20the%20healthcare%20system%20that%20has%20to%20be%20taken%20care%20of.%20More%20people%20will%20definitely%20come%20forward%20to%20donate%20the%20organs%20of%20loved%20ones%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20conviction.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20surgeon%2C%20I%20am%20deeply%20humbled%20to%20be%20part%20of%20this%20programme.%20During%20organ%20donations%2C%20I%20witness%20both%20ends%20of%20the%20spectrum%20%E2%80%93%20the%20profound%20grief%20of%20losing%20a%20loved%20one%20and%20the%20overwhelming%20joy%20and%20hope%20when%20a%20family%20member%20receives%20an%20o